column5: Have been staying at Wawa Motor Inn, but last time there found it a bit pricey. Any other ideas? I seem to recall a motel out on hiway 17 just west of town.
try Northernlights motel just west of Wawa, here is internet sitehttp://www.nlmotel.com/ jake
Try the Beaver Motel. Been staying there for years. Convenient, reasonable and great people.
We stay at the Bristol. It's always clean and reasonably priced.
